trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize"></xref> event of the <xref href="System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Gir dataene for den <xref href="System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize"> </xref> hendelsen til den <xref href="System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule"> </xref> klassen.

trans-unit.source: You can use the ProfileEventArgs class during the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize> event to specify a custom user profile.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke klassen ProfileEventArgs under den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize>-hendelsen for å angi en egendefinert brukerprofil.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize>

trans-unit.source: If, when the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize> event completes, the ProfileEventArgs parameter of the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventHandler> has its <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs.Profile%2A> property set to a value that’s not `null`, then the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> uses the value of the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs.Profile%2A> property in the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis, når den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize>hendelsen er fullført, parameteren ProfileEventArgs for den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventHandler>har den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs.Profile%2A>egenskapen satt til en verdi som ikke er `null`, den deretter <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule>bruker verdien for <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs.Profile%2A>egenskapen i gjeldende <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>.</xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs.Profile%2A> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs.Profile%2A> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventHandler> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize>

trans-unit.source: Creates an instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The ProfileEventArgs creates an instance of the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs> class and sets the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs.Context%2A> property to the specified <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>.
trans-unit.target: ProfileEventArgs oppretter en forekomst av <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs>klassen og startes, settes <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs.Context%2A>egenskapen til den angitte <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>.</xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs.Context%2A> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.HttpContext"></xref> of the current request.
Gets the <xref href="System.Web.HttpContext"></xref> for the current request.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.Web.HttpContext"> </xref> for gjeldende forespørsel.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs> object provides event information to the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize> event of the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> class.
The Context property provides access to the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> of the current request.
trans-unit.target: Context-egenskapen gir tilgang til den <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>til gjeldende forespørsel.</xref:System.Web.HttpContext>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.HttpContext"></xref> for the current request
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.HttpContext"> </xref> for den gjeldende forespørselen

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the user profile for the current request.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir brukerprofilen for gjeldende forespørsel.

trans-unit.source: You can use the Profile property during the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize> event to specify a custom user profile.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke profilegenskapen under den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize>-hendelsen for å angi en egendefinert brukerprofil.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize>

trans-unit.source: If, when the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize> event completes, the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs> parameter of the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventHandler> has its Profile property set to a value that’s not `null`, then the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> uses the value of the Profile property in the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis, når den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize>hendelsen er fullført, den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs>-parameteren for den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventHandler>har egenskapen profilen som er satt til en verdi som ikke er `null`, den deretter <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule>bruker verdien for egenskapen profil i gjeldende <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>.</xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventHandler> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> does not set the Profile property for the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize> event.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule>ikke angi egenskapen profilen for den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize>hendelsen.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> only gets the value of the Profile property when the code in the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize> event completes.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule>henter bare verdien for egenskapen profilen når koden i den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize>hendelsen er fullført.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule>

trans-unit.source: If the Profile property is not explicitly set by application code during the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize> event, the Profile property value will be `null`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis profilegenskapen ikke er eksplisitt angitt av programmet kode under den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize>hendelsen egenskapsverdien profilen blir `null`.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize>

trans-unit.source: The user profile to use for the current request.
trans-unit.target: Brukerprofil skal brukes til gjeldende forespørsel.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
